channel.title: Silab client lags so badly!
channel.description: Ok, so just about every place on the tele tab except for home lags your account so you can't log back in, I'm using Cryptchaos3 and I tried teleporting to the smithing area and got lagged out, thankfully I was on a test account but that's also why I made a new home and thieve area because every tele place lags you out and you can't get back on your account, got any advice on what I should put for a new smithing area? And a possible new mining area?
